{"tid":697510,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"［Rich tonight]富豪狂追，張曦雯突富貴晒百萬名車","createTime":"2018-06-11T04:10:21.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-12T16:34:52.000Z","uid":41351,"like":9,"dislike":30,"uniUserReply":76,"replies":[{"pid":"0b153827812d9d00eef1c696a957e0f29af1bd00","tid":697510,"uid":41351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-11T04:10:21.000Z","msg":"現年28歲的無綫新一代咪神張曦雯（Kelly），年前被踢爆與富二代Daniel相戀，不過最終分手收場。甩拖的Kelly未幾即獲城中富豪狂追，向來慳家的她近月還突然富貴，購下過百萬港元的新款保時捷，日前她便與「新歡」出巡尖沙咀，相約友人飯局！ <br />\n<br />\n曾奪國際中華小姐冠軍、擁有33C上圍的Kelly上月11日剛度過28歲生日，入行以來她曾與胡杏兒老公Philip、黃淑儀兒子徐肇平傳緋聞，年前則被踢爆與莊思明的富二代舊愛Daniel相戀，但據悉兩人早前已經分手。回復單身的Kelly今年初更透露身邊有追求者，過往低調戀情的她還心花怒放表示：「有人追，但係未搵到啱嘅，自己鍾意健康運動型。」 <br />\n<br />\n識歎四圍遊埠 <br />\n<br />\n原來桃花旺盛的Kelly，近月獲城中一名富豪熱烈追求，難怪最近她突然富貴不時四出遊埠，月前往美國探望親友後又往墨西哥等地旅行，上月還與母親到酒店歎Spa。生活「升呢」的Kelly出手零舍闊綽，平時出入以的士或租車代步的她，於4月尾一擲約120萬港元，購下了一部黑色的新款保時捷四驅車，新車更配上其姓氏及生日日期「511」作為車牌。 <br />\n<br />\n連日來Kelly更與「新歡」四處出巡，日前她在太古城工作後便匆匆步往停車場，期間不少男Fans上前要求合照，表現風騷的她有求必應，與Fans拍照後又再傾了一輪才往取車，她更細心執拾車尾箱一番，才駕駛新車返回電視城拍攝，及至晚上約9時，才見她驅車離開，直駛尖沙咀會合楊潮凱、黃嘉樂及譚凱琪等人晚膳。 <br />\n<br />\n楊潮凱幫睇位 <br />\n<br />\nKelly把座駕停泊於路邊車位時，楊潮凱幫她睇位後更搭着伊人香肩步入附近食肆醫肚，至凌晨約12時她才驅車返北角寓所。翌日下午3時許Kelly又出動，戴上帽、穿上短裙晒長腿的她，驅車直往九龍塘後即急急腳步入該處一個學會會館，逗留個多小時後才離開。 <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/11/120811_1f44de779254cb6355e9ede75679ab56.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F11%2F120811_1f44de779254cb6355e9ede75679ab56.png&h=dc075d60&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/11/120812_e0126a2c4bb22163cdafe1ae2349adde.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F11%2F120812_e0126a2c4bb22163cdafe1ae2349adde.png&h=40a30c13&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/11/120814_bfe0653b6d2f3275d53700d57bddf218.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F11%2F120814_bfe0653b6d2f3275d53700d57bddf218.png&h=3c34aed0&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"508cd5080b7192c26da2549adb3f776ec8d26f12","tid":697510,"uid":41351,"like":71,"dislike":1,"score":70,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-11T04:11:58.000Z","msg":"所以說做有錢人多好"},{"pid":"844e6ebc465931fb7b7b58904c795f0395c1673f","tid":697510,"uid":86030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-11T04:34:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc93884d194d54fbbcc8176534162c1dd07e8dac","tid":697510,"uid":63311,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-11T04:51:20.000Z","msg":"KC511?"},{"pid":"96826069d3a11122575c8285863d5f78babea4e3","tid":697510,"uid":35014,"like":27,"dislike":6,"score":21,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-11T05:01:02.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ab9407c1091096f6fc02bff41ec4d76cf4eeb8a0","tid":697510,"uid":129521,"like":175,"dislike":0,"score":175,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2018-06-11T05:12:47.000Z","msg":"佢個樣係上流人士嘅樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d3ad98e79c27aa05aabf9af1e4dff0a6aff3d367","tid":697510,"uid":139863,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-11T05:14:16.000Z","msg":"有無before圖？"},{"pid":"914f7556655f318cc740196a3d9956ddacd607cb","tid":697510,"uid":59602,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-11T05:23:46.000Z","msg":"咪神?"},{"pid":"1b377954abe0b4df2d3de1e3babd5d350ab56702","tid":697510,"uid":45213,"like":33,"dislike":1,"score":32,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-11T13:21:06.000Z","msg":"porn tonight<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6539be9e9dca5072d727dbff52f4d5e75243ca5a","tid":697510,"uid":51041,"like":4,"dislike":5,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-11T13:23:46.000Z","msg":"條女正撚到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/norm